links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/D1_l9hjzxxbABYuZ3Oar_tpe1Htsy723d_6ejQuNeTjzKhuTE9CCrzKKUJ09vUG39nTAMKpkM4Gj2TFKjLAs3Uwr1YCvz372-Ka-OT653Vg_nDGQJcuFL_AcM8tbpF3gkwIpktKjsBG7KLt3iSDXjY4FBd0df0wSixQY4PvszYBm7PNkhRGDYiRUQajXNM9w55KeFcS16s5px5e1z1BDcI_N5hM-pGmZZUxs5o_spkEUIOH61Yt6ssUHwcbNdUFzJKi-I4MNKj44icvb6sW64xY09kmrPHgrQNmqE5_10bNXYAI_j_6FPr7ildBf070BCIz5mKnqh-U/1S166v7X3LiyN17oNtN4F9Bk4bgzeQct/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="David Rovella - 总编辑：Bloomberg Digital |彭博社"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;大卫·E·罗维拉&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/xT6vjycihGTnROMqVxdwUmcdfvYB2Wo9Dm4yAAdO-chFDy7pmE4cJ9rJq_kkJwkH8fqilyhkAHFMYFqQABl_KlPfL5UegRY5f0varYsQ8WmGUeJHzIJjANRu3JJA1ugDiql-9a_3RZzaR3LEvy7xfID7jQVf091qCdvC012VmYVy6CTdRpdTkcuLpQvMHZlMTii0k8mvqKZNmHfU0sPfBIC52l6_m5I5_Igs8m74TNr962Vjqt0ZaFhg2xiA7O--ZWur9rHFM8wKw2uehvIWHPW-6rL8UB0oHLlNlaWSHfS314fWOYCFRbw2HfNBCkTS13CwkNX_gUi98q5ex3p_GywYBx8cqoQu1K07HmaQQtDnjSk6jmaOqDYuxSl0I6UOtaneeIPQ-8S9yciOK28F/zJ_1OUZBzpR8-N7INYxqfC_7YG7Sr4kT/20" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipk4c.6YE4mU/v1/-1x-1.jpg" alt=" " width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipk4c.6YE4mU/v1/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;特朗普在伊朗战争僵局中登陆中国&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;总统此次抵达是为了参加一次会议，这与他上次与习近平的中国峰会不同。这一次，中国国家主席正在挥舞稀土储备作为贸易战的大棒，而特朗普则在为摆脱伊朗战争而苦苦挣扎。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;由于能源价格飙升推高通胀（以及对通胀的预期&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;），投资者自 2007 年以来首次获得 5% 的 30 年期国债收益率&lt;/strong&gt;。拍卖结果表明，随着美国政府收益率达到近一年来的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/AFfck_K-jlsCn_EJLcJZt_0ubXFbfHvYh0qeesfazQqCejro8A_YFoLMIM8ZrxKomcZjtxSu_q2NE31vIoyYxu56yiWiA_IPtdQZ-AfkjlReYqpIC5CGIABJ-9A3dhPU9VPduoLtLpuTsvXfq_p8xEcS_8gD_B7qgZp67LhjSI5O6Ce56DPWYKswkmgOvtoWCUPDJ2_i01J1RvG1V7kfJTbGERzpwMNOLa0SpmCGL6v4farVi87Zi_Ww5_-F_HwH2hIVlZhidUkgejqdMbyMx24JQLARzj3V6F1Z-KBPii0z8lzDoVR3n27ln1Co7Ebn9lqAzHMR2LAWMBtYKq9stenWR6RD2atqwYjqkJK01jeiwqEjVNiWR3FsB1IsVp-XH5uoJ5w2riHJCtxh2Ul4mwY3O_GJ3Rz8GI39MzZYJCNY5jYGSxAJ2OP0b0O__NAqi70oD4yL1IJA6r1pBc6kY_rlZ-0TGCKRwiTSMyOwXlgAQWYelHMgV8FmqRLAwzBhbDhEwFBwgNBuGtC6smRtvjXwMSK8fuw/7jLNzTCBZ7KPax9OhUdv0I00-e3_whPo/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="通胀担忧导致收益率升至 2026 年高位，债券投资者纷纷逃离"&gt;最高水平，&lt;/a&gt;市场需求中等。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;德意志银行(Deutsche Bank)利率策略师史蒂文·曾(Steven Zeng)表示：“我预计收益率达到5%时就会出现投资者需求。” “这通常是 30 年期国债对养老基金和其他负债驱动型投资者更具吸引力的地方。”然而，不确定因素&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/yW4Yc-JsVWFPxho6G1_sqpOAOHqgE43lEDLztMeoE3hIOy1mg-i8XhZOf4X_rsXt3FcHAvOcNfV29F9KtL1YdxSd6jHam7NMGJGcZsWI-79iXP6x4CwaYWeyqw3M7E9Q2GygyDHM5mlN92OWjtVNJPWiffzGVdYBcTKHPP6ys0gtscJcFlAuWV0a7gIiTDy0zmf5mIbVYK1Y0gvB97uaVh4qsxY6_wLli1NzE0b8n8cumD_w_HlJcM9qBXZfPj47fIEa7wNc9WRFSLqU2fikbjWK71RqnitZkvT8hM8sMuNhnKI6DWbQKgQPe